{"timestamp": "2025-12-06 08:48:17.223638", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission complete.\n\nSummary:\n- Anomaly detected: Yes\n- Faulty device(s): web_server_0 (10.200.0.3)\n- Root cause: sender_application_delay\n\nRationale:\n- Elevated and erratic HTTP TTFB (~3.3–3.5 s) is isolated to web_server_0 while network latency and loss are normal, OSPF/DNS healthy, and other servers plus the load balancer perform normally. This points to application-side processing delay on web_server_0 rather than a network issue.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 1916, "output_tokens": 115, "total_tokens": 2031, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1792}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
